        android:textAppearance="?android:attr/textAppearanceSmall"
        android:text="1 Velocity of sound\n
2 Frequency of sound \n
3 Intensity of sound \n
4 Intensity level \n
5 Acoustic pressure\n
6 Pitch of sound\n
7 Timbre of sound\n
8 Echo \n
9 Reverberation and reverberation time\n
10 Reflection of sound
"
